import React, { useEffect } from 'react' const Office = () => { useEffect(()=>{ (document).ready(function() { ("#myCarousel").on("slide.bs.carousel", function(e) { var $e = $(e.relatedTarget); var idx = $e.index(); var itemsPerSlide = 4; var totalItems = $(".carousel-item").length; if (idx >= totalItems - (itemsPerSlide - 1)) { var it = itemsPerSlide - (totalItems - idx); for (var i = 0; i < it; i++) { // append slides to end if (e.direction == "left") { $(".carousel-item") .eq(i) .appendTo(".carousel-inner"); } else { $(".carousel-item") .eq(0) .appendTo($(this).find(".carousel-inner")); } } } }); }); },[]) return (
